"title": "8811: riches, believers' attitudes towards",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "8811: riches, believers' attitudes towards",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>God entrusts some of his people with material wealth.  If this is to be a blessing, it must be used in God-honouring ways.</p>\n<h2>Believers may be blessed with riches</h2>\n<h3>Riches can be a blessing from God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr29:16\">1CH 29:16</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr29:14-1Chr29:15\">1CH 29:14–29:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job1:9-Job1:102\">JOB 1:9–1:102</a>KI <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job4:1\">4:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt8:20\">MAT 8:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke6:20\">LUK 6:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke16:20-Luke16:22\">LUK 16:20–16:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom15:26\">ROM 15:26</a></p>\n<h2>The attitude of believers towards riches</h2>\n<h3>They acknowledge that their riches come from God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr29:12\">1CH 29:12</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl5:19-Eccl5:20\">ECC 5:19–5:20</a></p>\n<h3>They devote their riches to God's service</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov3:9-Prov3:10\">PRO 3:9–3:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr29:1-1Chr29:9\">1CH 29:1–29:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts4:32-Acts4:37\">ACT 4:32–4:37</a></p>\n<h3>They support gospel work and workers</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke8:1-Luke8:3\">LUK 8:1–8:3</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts16:15\">ACT 16:15</a></p>\n<h3>They give to the poor</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John3:17\">1JN 3:17</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke19:8\">LUK 19:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts9:36-Acts9:39\">ACT 9:36–9:39</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal2:10\">GAL 2:10</a></p>\n<h3>They are generous</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim6:18\">1TI 6:18</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut15:10-Deut15:11\">DEU 15:10–15:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor9:10-2Cor9:11\">2CO 9:10–9:11</a></p>\n<h3>They remain humble</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas1:10-Jas1:11\">JAS 1:10–1:11</a></p>\n<h3>They do not trust in riches</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim6:17\">1TI 6:17</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job31:24-Job31:28\">JOB 31:24–31:28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov11:28\">PRO 11:28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer49:4\">JER 49:4</a></p>\n<h3>They do not set their heart on riches</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps62:10\">PSA 62:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke12:29-Luke12:30\">LUK 12:29–12:30</a></p>\n<h2>Believers value heavenly riches most</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt6:20-Matt6:21\">MAT 6:20–6:21</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke12:33-Luke12:34\">LUK 12:33–12:34</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim6:18-1Tim6:19\">1TI 6:18–6:19</a></p>\n<h2>Examples of rich believers</h2>\n<h3>Abraham</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen12:1-Gen12:3\">GEN 12:1–12:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen13:1-Gen13:2\">GEN 13:1–13:2</a></p>\n<h3>Solomon</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr1:11-2Chr1:12\">2CH 1:11–1:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr9:22\">2CH 9:22</a></p>\n<h3>Hezekiah</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr32:27-2Chr32:29\">2CH 32:27–32:29</a></p>\n<h3>Job</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job1:1-Job1:3\">JOB 1:1–1:3</a></p>\n<h3>Joseph of Arimathea</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa53:9\">ISA 53:9</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt27:57-Matt27:60\">MAT 27:57–27:60</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark15:42-Mark15:46\">MRK 15:42–15:46</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke23:50-Luke23:54\">LUK 23:50–23:54</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John19:38-John19:42\">JHN 19:38–19:42</a></p>",
